data.message:
Happy Birthday Sydni I know I'm late but to express my graditude to you, I decided to write you a cheesy heart felt poem. 

Sydni Sydni Sydni
If you were an organ
You'd be my kidney 
Could I survive without you? 
Maybe temporarily
But it forsure wouldn't be easy
Easy breezy Lemon Squeezy 
G-eezy got Nothing on Weezy 
But none of em got nothing on you hun
You'll always be number one! 
Sydni Green Sydni Green!
You're a a bluish eyed, curly haired queen!
We've been all the way to lick and back.
Been through a lot, deep convos before I hit the sack.
Always been there when I needed you Laughed at my bad jokes on cue.
We're steady riding Bart late at night
Never mattered how dark
You're smiles just to bright!
I've had some cloudy days
But your deep sunny gaze
Lights up the world for days. 
Been dating my Antonio for a min now
And just gotta say la bond is tooo strong
Can only be compared to King Kong!
You two might be my greatest creation
Perfect for one another, no other temptation
But for yall I can't take full accountibility
Wasn't easy, shout out to my girl Michele Gee
Antonio and Sydni?
Now those are some household names 
And naw they ain't in it for the fame
I know this poem is a little late
But something told me you're bday wasn't the right time
Maybe it was fate?
Alright well that's it for now
Hope this poem made you smile
Taalib's out, Kachow!

i love you <3 happy 18th
